node.text: Both Gia Peppers and Danielle Young are journalists and hosts who were selected to take over social media pages of @jennymollen and @iamcattsadler today! Listen and watch as they share theirs experiences, their thoughts on living through and using their voices for to support the #blacklivesmatter movement, and what their hopes are for their own dreams and what this world could look like after real change. 🙏🏾❤️
